articles.title: 53 of 65 Omicron cases detected in Singapore as at Monday arrived via VTL - The Star Online
articles.description: SINGAPORE (The Straits Times/Asia News Network): Fifty-three of the 65 confirmed imported Omicron cases detected in Singapore as at Monday (Dec 20) had arrived via the vaccinated travel lane (VTL), said the Ministry of Health (MOH).
